						<summary>

						<p>Sculptured stone (fourth) set up near the tank bund.</p>						

						<p>This damaged and undated epigraph may be assigned to about the 9th century A.D., on the basis of palaeography.</p>						

						<p>Badly damaged and covered by the roots of a banyan tree. It mentions Bhīmarāja.</p>						

